name: Playsuit
description:
Beautiful 100% cotton yellow and blue floral playsuit.

This playsuit with elasticised waisted is finshed with a contrasting trim to the shorts, tie strap and removable button brooch.  Tis roomy design allows for variations in height and the option for an undershirt for the more sun concious. This is sure to be a favourite in any girls' wardrobe even a tom girl!

name: Slip Dress
description: Beautiful 100% cotton designer fabric is allowed to show off with this classic slip dress style.  The adjustable strap allows the dress to sit lower on the chest or higher towards the neck, thus a short dress or longer dress.  The adjustable straps also allow room for our fast growing childern.  The style can also be worn as a top for an older girl! Classic cool dress for a hot summer!
